    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"536\">Extinction Drive (Action; 1/Long Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"539\" />You become the embodiment of the hunt.</p><p data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"678\">As an action, you enter a state of absolute predation for <strong data-start=\"637\" data-end=\"649\">1 minute</strong>. While this state is active:</p><ul data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"901\"><li data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-start=\"682\" data-end=\"727\">Your movement speed increases by <strong data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"726\">10 feet</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"813\"><p data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"813\">You have <strong data-start=\"739\" data-end=\"752\">advantage</strong> on all <strong data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"776\">melee weapon</strong> and <strong data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"799\">natural weapon</strong> attack rolls.</p></li><li data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"901\"><p data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"901\"><strong data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"833\">Once per turn</strong>, when you hit a creature, you may deal <strong data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"900\">+1d10 additional damage</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"928\"><strong data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"928\">When this state ends:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"1011\"><li data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"966\"><p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"966\">You gain <strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"966\">2 levels of exhaustion</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"967\" data-end=\"1011\"><p data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"1011\">Your <strong data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"987\">Rage ends</strong> immediately (if active)</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1097\">Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"1083\" data-end=\"1096\">long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1102\" /><p data-start=\"1104\" data-end=\"1162\"><br /><code data-start=\"1125\" data-end=\"1162\">[GAROU_FEATURE] id=extinction-drive</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"536\">Extinction Drive (Action; 1/Long Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"539\" />You become the embodiment of the hunt.</p><p data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"678\">As an action, you enter a state of absolute predation for <strong data-start=\"637\" data-end=\"649\">1 minute</strong>. While this state is active:</p><ul data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"901\"><li data-start=\"680\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-start=\"682\" data-end=\"727\">Your movement speed increases by <strong data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"726\">10 feet</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"813\"><p data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"813\">You have <strong data-start=\"739\" data-end=\"752\">advantage</strong> on all <strong data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"776\">melee weapon</strong> and <strong data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"799\">natural weapon</strong> attack rolls.</p></li><li data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"901\"><p data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"901\"><strong data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"833\">Once per turn</strong>, when you hit a creature, you may deal <strong data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"900\">+1d10 additional damage</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"928\"><strong data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"928\">When this state ends:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"1011\"><li data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"966\"><p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"966\">You gain <strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"966\">2 levels of exhaustion</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"967\" data-end=\"1011\"><p data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"1011\">Your <strong data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"987\">Rage ends</strong> immediately (if active)</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1097\">Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"1083\" data-end=\"1096\">long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"1099\" data-end=\"1102\" /><p data-start=\"1104\" data-end=\"1162\"></p>"
